Ndị egwuregwu ahụ họọrọ Tremaglio iji dochie Michele Roberts na Septemba 22, 2021, wee banye n'ọrụ ahụ mgbe Roberts lara ezumike nká na mbido Jenụwarị 2022. Tupu ọ banye na NBPA dị ka onye isi nchịkwa, Tremaglio, onye lara ezumike nká na Deloitte LLP, jere ozi dị ka onye nchịkwa maka ụlọ ọrụ Deloitte Greater Washington.
Mary's County, Maryland. Tremaglio nwetara akara ugo mmụta Bachelor of Arts na Mahadum Mount St
Mary na Business & Finance na 1992. Ọ natara JD na Mahadum Maryland School of Law na MBA na Mahadụ Baltimore. Nne Tremaglio, Pamela Langley, gara Mahadum Morgan State.
Tremaglio sonyeere Deloitte na Nọvemba 2010 ma họpụta ya dịka onye isi nchịkwa maka mpaghara Greater Washington na 2017. O mechara sonye na NBPA dị ka onye isi nchịkwa.

A kpọrọ Tremaglio onye isi onye mmekọ nke afọ na 2019 site na Washington Business Journal ma họrọ ya dị ka otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị 150 kachasị ike na Washington na 2019 na 2021 site na Washingtonian Magazine. N'afọ 2020, Tremaglio natara onyinye Triple-Impact Executive Award site na Positive Coaching Alliance.
